│  Next.js 16 UI │  ────►│  FastAPI Agent :8000│  ────►│  SQL Server 2022 │
│  React 19      │       │  - /connect         │       │  (Docker)        │
│  Tailwind 4    │       │  - /query           │       │  AdventureWorks  │
│  Port :3000    │       │  - /services/*      │       │  :1433           │
└────────────────┘       └──────────┬──────────┘       └──────────────────┘
                                    │
                         ┌──────────┴──────────┐
                         ▼                     ▼
                ┌─────────────────┐   ┌────────────────────┐
                │  RAG Knowledge  │   │  OpenAI APIs       │
                │  Base (offline) │   │  - GPT-4o (reason) │
                │  1536-dim       │   │  - GPT-4o-mini     │
                │  embeddings     │   │  - text-embedding  │
                └─────────────────┘   │    -3-small        │
                                      └────────────────────┘
```

**Two-phase engine:**
- **Pre-Plan** (offline, once): extract schema → LLM narrative analysis → embed into a vector store.
- **Post-Plan** (runtime, every query): 6-step agentic pipeline — refine → semantic search → graph expand → blueprint → draft-critic loop → NL synthesis.

