## Benchmark: Validated Against a Published Reference

I benchmarked NexusChat against the canonical 12-question AdventureWorks analysis from [*Exploring AdventureWorks2019 Database using SQL* (Iyanu Olatunji, Medium)](https://medium.com/@iyanuolatunji21/exploring-adventureworks2019-database-using-sql-fdffac5d8b25).

The article contains **hand-written SQL by a human data analyst** for 12 business questions covering the entire sales schema. For each question, I gave NexusChat the plain-English version of the question — nothing else — and compared its autonomously-generated SQL and numerical results to the reference.

| Question Theme                       | Joins Required | NexusChat Result   |
| :----------------------------------- | :------------- | :----------------- |
| Sales by product category            | 5 tables       | Match              |
| Seasonal sales trends                | 2 tables       | Match              |
| Top sales representatives            | 1 table        | Match              |
| Cross-sell / up-sell opportunities   | Self-join + CTE| Match              |
| Products with highest units sold     | 2 tables       | Match              |
| Highest-revenue region               | 2 tables       | Match              |
| Territory purchasing behaviour       | 3 tables       | Match              |
| Product popularity per region        | 3 tables + RANK| Match              |
| Top spending customers               | 4 tables       | Match              |
| Online vs in-person channels         | 1 table + CASE | Match              |
| Most profitable products             | 2 tables       | Match              |
| Overall yearly sales performance     | 1 table        | Match              |

**All 12 questions produced the same numerical results as the reference analyst's hand-written queries.** Full execution traces — refined queries, cosine scores, iteration histories, Critic verdicts, timings — are captured in a [public validation log spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1baeedstrM9wZqRiRsaW7h1oVU3f0RoY24nAsww6WnEs/edit?gid=527362238#gid=527362238).

